---
name: ssh_agent
description: Manage loaded SSH keys with ssh-agent and ssh-add — load a key so you type its passphrase once, list the loaded keys, and remove them. Use to stop being prompted for a key passphrase every connection, or to check which keys the agent holds.
kind: tool
tags: [ssh, agent, ssh-add, keys, passphrase, identity]
use_when: [stop being asked for my ssh passphrase, add a key to the ssh agent, list loaded ssh keys, ssh-add, load a private key, remove keys from the agent]
